      <section eId="sec_82_09">
        <num>82.09</num>
        <heading>Facilitation of agreement</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_82_09__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>through</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_82_09__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of\nsection 82.12 of this article shall only apply in circumstances where a\ndecision is made by a decision-maker pursuant to a supported\ndecision-making agreement created in accordance with this article where\nsuch decision-maker and his or her supporter or supporters have worked\nwith a facilitator, such supporter or supporters have followed a\nrecognized supported decision-making facilitation or education process\nas defined and prescribed by regulations promulgated by the office for\npeople with developmental disabilities and such facilitator has signed\nsuch agreement.\n  * NB Effective 90 days from the date that the regulations issued in\naccordance with ยง 1 of chapter 481 of 2022 appear in the New York State\nRegister or the date such regulations are adopted, whichever is later.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
